code: @Override protected void doHealthCheck(Health.Builder builder) throws Exception {     Select select = QueryBuilder.select("release_version").from("system", "local").     ResultSet results = this.cassandraOperations.getCqlOperations().queryForResultSet(select).     if (results.isExhausted()) {         builder.up().         return.     }     String version = results.one().getString(0).     builder.up().withDetail("version", version). }
